dhRuva  tALa
duritavana kuTAri durjana kula vairi
sharaNAgata vajrapaMjara kuMjara
vara saMrakShaka janma maraNarahita mahita
parama karuNAsiMdhu BaktabaMdhu
svarata svataMtra jagadBarita citsuKapUrNa
hariyE kSharAkShara puruShOttama
urugAya vaikuMTha vara maMdira caMdira
taraNi kOTi saMkAsha vimala kEsha
duradoLagarjunana turaga naDesida shaM
kara BayaMkara lOkaika vIra
narasiMha ninna pAdakkeragi bEDikoMbe
morehokka dAsage baMda Bayava pari
harisi sauKyava karuNisu dayadiMda
sarvaraMtaryAmi lOkasvAmi
smaraNe mAtradi ajAmiLage muktiyanitte
aridEnO nInIga porevudemma
saruva kAmada jagannAthaviTThala Bakta
paripAlakaneMba birudu ninnadallave? ||
maTTa tALa
vidhipita nInallade nidhipatigaLuMTe?
sadananAgi ippe ninna dAsarigAgi
madhusUdhana jagannAthaviTThalarEya
nidhananenisikoMbe ninna dvEShigaLige ||

rUpaka  tALa
mUru lOkasvAmi sarvajna suKapUrNa
prEraka sAkShi kAraNakArya dOShavi
dUra sadguNasAMdra sajjanAMbudhi caMdra
BArakarta jagake nInire emma manOratha
salisuvudEnasAdhyavO ninage?
krUramAnavara saMhAramADisu guru
mArutaniMdati shIGravAgi
nIrakShiseMdu prArthisuve Baktarige BUri
sAra BAgyavanittu kRupemADu anudina
shUra jagannAthaviTThala nInalladi
nnAru Baktara kAva karuNigaLu jagadi? ||
JuMpethALapitaniMda noMda prahlAdananu kAyde dE
vategaLige baMda Baya parihariside drau
padiya more kELi divyAMbarava karuNiside
kShitijanAlayadi baLaluva bAleyara dvArA
vatige karedoydu olidavara pOShiside mA
rutiya karadiM bRuhadratakuvarana kolisi
pRuthivipara biDisi pAliside karuNadali kuru
pRuthanadoL pAMDavara gelisi kIrtiya paDede
shatamOdanastradiMdali garBadhoLage pI
DitanAda shishuparIkShitana saMtaiside
shitikaMThagolidu sAyakanAgi muppurada
satiyaranolisi kIrutiyitte Baktanige
mitiyuMTe ninna karuNake dEvapati sAM
prata bEDikoMbe binnapa kELajasra saM
stutipa Bakutara manOrathava pUraisu su
vratanAma shrIjagannAthaviTThala BAga
vata janara priya nInE gati emage ihaparadi ||

tripuTa  tALa
