hAsanavannErisi nI poredeyo pa
rAsharAtmaja ninna guNagaLa baNNise
nA samarthane eMdeMdigAdaru dEva
nI sulaBaneMdAshrayisiMdu nA bi
nnaisideno I rItiyalli saru
vAsunilaya shrIjagannAthaviTThalarEya
Isu mAtugaLEke manmanada
Ashe pUrtiya mADi emmanu dayadi u
dAsisade anudina nOLpudu ||
aTTa tALa
